  "Qtext": "\n A rectangular water tank has length 5 m, breadth 12 m and capacity \\(240 m^3\\). \n A model of the water tank is to made with capacity of \\(1920 cm^3\\). Find\\\\\n (i) the dimensions of the model\\\\\n (ii) the ratio of the total surface area of the tank to that model.\\\\\n",
